Richards Bay Coal Terminal CEO Said to Quit, Miningmx Reports

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-10-04T15:11:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/richards-bay-coal-terminal-ceo-said-to-quit-miningmx-reports.html
Richards Bay Coal Terminal Chief
Executive Officer Raymond Chirwa plans to resign tomorrow,
Johannesburg-based online news agency Miningmx said, citing
unidentified people in the industry.  Chirwa’s mobile phone and Richards Bay office line were on
voicemail when Bloomberg News called. Spokeswoman Zama Luthuli
couldn’t immediately comment when Bloomberg reached her on her
mobile phone today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  